    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334430/extras/4660b3224e4895524e55bd4d1c665ad1.avif?t=1745942972\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334430/extras/17287724e2fcd3c894dc947ba649ead5.poster.avif?t=1745942972\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334430/extras/17287724e2fcd3c894dc947ba649ead5.webm?t=1745942972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334430/extras/17287724e2fcd3c894dc947ba649ead5.mp4?t=1745942972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>反抗军的制造技能越来越有创意了！他们利用在Östertörn各地找到的零件和技术制作了一批新的野战装备，帮助自己与机器兽作战！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334430/extras/bbb12e91e063a1d3396d9adfe0c7c61a.avif?t=1745942972\" width=616 height=256 /></span><br><br>第二款Tactical Equipment Pack中有5种全新装备物品供玩家使用：<br><br>• <strong>玩具车诱饵</strong>：一辆改装的遥控车，上面绑有照明弹和无线电。车放到地上之后就会以最快速度开走，伴随着燃烧的信号弹，收音机的音量也会开到最大。这种诱饵很适合在胶着战况下将敌人引开。<br>• <strong>感官干扰器</strong>：启动时产生一个经过特殊调谐的电磁场，会干扰机器兽的感官，但对玩家无影响。<br>• <strong>黑客飞镖</strong>：一个用磁铁和黑客装置改装的草坪飞镖，投掷距离很远，同时又很精确，用来在相对安全的情况下对敌人进行打击。飞镖击中机器兽之后可破坏其敌友识别系统，令其对其他机器兽发起攻击。这种效果一直会持续到该装备的电池耗尽。<br>• <strong>遥控蜱虫</strong>：这个经过改装的蜱虫已经重置了导航系统，可以使用遥控汽车的发射器控制。为了稳妥起见，它的身上还安装了一个自制的铁管炸弹。这样就可以直接控制蜱虫，把它送到毫无防备的机器兽中进行侦察，并伺机炸毁敌人。<br>• <strong>便携式制导炮塔</strong>：一种对付地面和目标的有力武器，可以发射3枚小型火箭推进式榴弹。这些榴弹可自动制导，锁定附近的目标。只要有一个炮塔处于活动状态，机器兽就别想安生。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334430/extras/f0fbaa1a9676b181e72c4d06c4969237.poster.avif?t=1745942972\" width=616 height=256 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334430/extras/f0fbaa1a9676b181e72c4d06c4969237.webm?t=1745942972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2334430/extras/f0fbaa1a9676b181e72c4d06c4969237.mp4?t=1745942972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
